quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  12,5,"“(Bambo wake) adati: “E iwe mwana wanga! Usawasimbire abale ako maloto ako (kuopa kuti) angakuchitire chiwembu; ndithu satana kwa munthu, ndi mdani woonekera.”"
  12,6,"““Ndipo momwemo Mbuye wako akusankha komanso akuphunzitsa kumasulira nkhani (za maloto) ndi kukwaniritsa mtendere Wake pa iwe, ndi pa mbumba ya Ya’qub monga momwe adakwaniritsira kwa makolo ako kale, Ibrahim ndi Ishaq. Ndithu Mbuye wako Ngodziwa, Ngwanzeru zakuya.”"
  12,7,"“Ndithu mwa Yûsuf ndi abale ake, muli malingaliro ambiri kwa ofunsa (zinthu kuti adziwe)"
  12,8,"“Kumbuka pamene (abale a Yûsuf) adati: “Ndithu Yûsuf ndi m’bale wake (Binyamini) ngokondeka zedi kwa bambo wathu kuposa ife pomwe ife ndife gulu lamphamvu. Ndithu bambo wathu ali mkusokera koonekera (sadziwa yemwe ali ndi chithandizo chokwanira).”"
  12,9,"““Mupheni Yûsuf kapena mukamponye ku dziko (lakutali), kuti nkhope ya bambo wanu ikutembenukireni (pakuti nthawi imeneyo Yûsuf sadzakhalapo, yemwe akumkonda kwambiriyo); ndipo pambuyo pake (mutalapa tchimoli) mdzakhala abwino, (kwa Allah).”"
  12,10,"“Adanena wonena mwa iwo: “Musamuphe Yûsuf, koma mponyeni m’chitsime chakuya; adzamtola ena a paulendo ngati inu mwalingadi kutelo.”"
  12,11,"“(Pambuyo pogwirizana paganizo lomuponya m’chitsime chakuya adapita kwa bambo wawo) anati: “E bambo wathu! Kodi bwanji simutikhulupirira pa Yûsuf, pomwe ife timamfunira zabwino?”"
  12,12,"“Mperekeni mawa pamodzi ndi ife (kubusa) kuti akadye mokondwa ndi kusewera; ndithudi, ife tikamsamala.”"
  12,13,"“(Bambo wawo) adati: “Ndithu zikundidandaulitsa zakuti mupite naye; ndikuopa kuti angajiwe ndi mimbulu pomwe inu simukulabadira za iye.”"
  12,14,"“(Iwo) adati: “Ngati mimbulu itamudya pomwe ife ndife gulu lanyonga kwambiri, ndiye kuti tidzakhala otaika.”"